room_title: Escape room "Grandma's Surprise" by Trapped! Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 173 Village Ct Ste 105, San Dimas, CA 91773
room_description: Today is your Grandmother’s 100th birthday! The whole family is getting together to pay her a surprise visit and throw her a party. However, Grandma doesn’t appear to be home. You and the others may just be the ones getting a surprise today!
